text: Seitse ('Seven') was a private Estonian television channel. It includes culture and music for Estonians and Russians of ages 25–45. Music channel Seitse showed at least 400 music videos per day. ==History== The channel closed its activities on 31 December 2016.Midagi muusikasõpradele!
